maybe `` you had to be there ... '' i ca n't imagine why mr. andriessen 's new opera writing to vermeer is garnering so much praise -- maybe `` you had to be there . '' on cd , however , it 's a grating , annoying , and self-consciously postmodern trial to endure ... in fact , i finally had to just give up about halfway through the second disc . life is too short , after all .